profile: We are Tip Top Tapers Drywall, we are located in Woodstock ON. We offer all services when it comes to drywall finishing. We offer repairs, texture ceilings, specialty work, resurface work, rush jobs, quick repairs, new build, renovation,and emergency work. We also do insurance work. Call us before you try and scrape that old texture off. We have a solution. We offer priming and painting of the finished drywall at an additional cost. We are fast and efficient when it comes to our work. Check out our Facebook page to see examples, just type Tip Top Tapers Drywall the Facebook search bar. For more information and a free quote, do not hesitate to call or text 519-536-3299 ask for Colt We now accept credit card payment at your door. Master Card, Visa, American Express and Discover.
